{"TopicId":68864,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Just love the lights","CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T03:47:05Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T03:47:05Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI think the adding of colors (or tints) to the lights is the best thing since sliced fuel tanks! The possibilities and combinations are just endless. I know it\u0027s a very trivial addition to the game but, being a poor pilot but a pretty good designer (in my mind), I have already spent countless hours on various light configurations on numerous crafts. To me it adds an extra ooh, awe and whoa to this game!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RocketPilot573","CreatedById":62803,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T03:51:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI use them for adding nav lights to planes, and I can FINALLY get rid of that huge glare that the more powerful lights make.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NASAFanboy","CreatedById":57300,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T12:54:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWait, when did they add sliced fuel tanks?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"DeepSpaceDutch","CreatedById":66213,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T13:09:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpacedCowboy\u0022 data-cite=\u0022SpacedCowboy\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ETo me it adds an extra ooh, awe and whoa to this game!\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EHear hear!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://cloud-3.steampowered.com/ugc/3298066830147314600/06BADB170AE7BBA1166965C68A502F6244CDF2FE/\u0022 alt=\u002206BADB170AE7BBA1166965C68A502F6244CDF2FE\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xeldrak","CreatedById":57228,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T13:42:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWait, what? \u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThe lights can now be colored?!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Milkshakefiend","CreatedById":70644,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:15:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Xeldrak\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Xeldrak\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWait, what? \u003Cp\u003EThe lights can now be colored?!\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ERight click on lights in the VAB/SPH and tweak til beautiful!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/HZ6nNrll.png\u0022 alt=\u0022HZ6nNrll.png\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:18:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ECan you modify them in flight?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI didn\u0027t know this until very recently, haven\u0027t had a chance to do it yet.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Othuyeg","CreatedById":105454,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:31:51Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMy space station is going disco now.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kinglet","CreatedById":58832,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:32:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwhip\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Starwhip\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003ECan you modify them in flight?\u003Cp\u003EI didn\u0027t know this until very recently, haven\u0027t had a chance to do it yet.\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EYes, you can! \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:43:39Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E Yay! I must put Port/Starboard lights on ALL THE THINGS!\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps someone could make a Kerbal disco?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Othuyeg","CreatedById":105454,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T14:45:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwhip\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Starwhip\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E Yay! I must put Port/Starboard lights on ALL THE THINGS!\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps someone could make a Kerbal disco?\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI am on it.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alymon","CreatedById":106720,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T15:14:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI love that lights can be colored now. I made a rover (sort of) that is basically just a giant light tower with action groups to trigger different colors. It\u0027s fun!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ArmchairGravy","CreatedById":78526,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T15:18:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ENow if we had a strobe slider, they would be perfect.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Xacktar","CreatedById":88876,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T15:18:54Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwhip\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Starwhip\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E Yay! I must put Port/Starboard lights on ALL THE THINGS!\u003Cp\u003EPerhaps someone could make a Kerbal disco?\u003C/p\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://youtu.be/puIoRpRCCHs\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003EWay ahead of you.\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"engraverwilliam","CreatedById":52621,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T15:36:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003Ecan we somehow shrink the light fixtures themselves?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NecroBones","CreatedById":105424,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T15:45:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022engraverwilliam\u0022 data-cite=\u0022engraverwilliam\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003Ecan we somehow shrink the light fixtures themselves?\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI would also like for the front of the lamp to colorize to match the illumination, as that would be more realistic, and make it easier to use them as running/navigation lights.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Othuyeg","CreatedById":105454,"CreatedDateTime":"2014-04-10T16:00:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EThe gentlemen\u0027s club \u0022Green Unicorn\u0022 is where Jeb and the boys hang out when they are not in space.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThese men work hard and they play harder.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022http://www.twitch.tv/othuyeg/b/518657632\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ehttp://www.twitch.tv/othuyeg/b/518657632\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}